citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Access and inspection of records and property.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00-2:00 PM
on 12/03/2014. No one was home upon arrival and the licensee was reached by cell phone. It was determined that
the licensee was at work and unable to be present for the inspection.
